data.description: Welcome to your exquisite new residence in the award-winning Rancho Mission Viejo community! Nestled directly across from The Sendero Guest House Pool, Putting Green, and Dog Park, this Shea-designed open floorplan is a pinnacle of luxury and convenience. Not only does this gem boast 3 spacious bedrooms and a bonus tv room – one of which is conveniently located downstairs – but it also offers a versatile office space upstairs, ensuring ample room for both relaxation and productivity. A standout feature of its prime Sendero location is its significantly lower Mello Roos compared to Esencia, enhancing its desirability. The homeowner's attention to detail shines through with bespoke upgrades such as: completely repainted interior, end unit with so much light, tons of upgrades throughout, Thermador side-by-side refrigerator/freezer, 36" Bertazzoni Italian range, 72 bottle element by Vinotenp 6' by 8' wine refrigerator with double drawers below, elegant tile porcelain wall, custom kitchen countertop, a distinctive Kohler sink atop an acacia base in the powder room, dual 5 ft. Napolean fireplaces in both the living and primary spaces, impressive 84” ceiling fans, bidet-equipped toilets, tailored cabinetry, ample storage in the garage, including built-in units and racks, and so much more. Seller’s are willing to remove the jacuzzi to open up the back yard space. They are also willing to install/add upper Kitchen Cabinets to match existing lower cabinets, and add a pantry remodel or give a credit of $5400. As a Rancho Mission Viejo resident, you gain exclusive access to amenities across the Villages of Sendero, Esencia, Rienda, and future developments. Dive into resort-style pools, enroll your children in the esteemed Esencia K-8 school, engage in community farming, and maintain an active lifestyle with state-of-the-art fitness centers. And for leisure, enjoy the putting green, bocce ball courts, tennis and pickle ball courts, playgrounds, coffee shop, fire pits, and a vibrant arcade, among other delights. Get ready to create lasting memories in this beautiful home, where your dreams become reality. Welcome to your new life in Rancho Mission Viejo!
